Remember Me Nine Muses' Kyung Li shows off her moves on 'Laws of the Jungle' By KpopJoA 1 hour ago 4,004 256 3 1 Google+ Broadcasted on February 24, the members of SBS' 'Laws of the Jungle' traveled to a remote island off Sulawesi, Indonesia where they each received red onion nets as part of their survival gear.
While on the boat, fellow member Kim Young Chul thought of a brilliant idea and told Kyung Li , "Hey, try these on." 
With that, captain Kim Byung Man like the gentleman he is knelt and carefully slipped the net over her legs, soon a fashion runway was held on the boat with Kyung Li posing with the new item turning them into fashionable onion boots, making the members go wild.
